reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 21, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Awesome power supply for Dell 8930
reviews.reviewText: This fit perfectly. Beware there are other brands without cables, this one includes all the needed cables. I’m not sure how you’d even reattach your existing cable to a power supply that doesn’t include the cables. Other commentators have noted the included cables weren’t long enough - they certainly are but make sure you take a few photos so you don’t route them wrong.
